When you complete a task:
- Write a summary to `.workflow/STATUS.md` (what you did, what files you changed, any blockers)
- Do NOT update `AGENT_LEDGER.md` — that's CC's job
- If you hit an error you can't resolve, write it to `.workflow/STATUS.md` under "Blockers" and stop
